BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Introduction) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Intermittent fasting \(IF\) is not a diet - it's an eating pattern that cycles between) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (periods of fasting and eating. It focuses on WHEN you eat rather than WHAT you eat.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (Research shows benefits for weight loss, metabolic health, brain function, and longevity.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
