stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Chapter 2: Choosing Your Method) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Popular IF Methods Compared) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 642.4 Td (16:8 \(Most Popular - Recommended for Beginners\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 626.4 Td (- Fast for 16 hours, eat within 8-hour window) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 612.4 Td (- Example: Eat 12pm-8pm, fast 8pm-12pm) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 598.4 Td (- Difficulty: Easy to moderate) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 584.4 Td (- Best for: Beginners, daily practice, sustainable lifestyle) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 556.6 Td (18:6 \(Intermediate\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 540.6 Td (- Fast for 18 hours, eat within 6-hour window) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 526.6 Td (- Example: Eat 1pm-7pm) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 512.6 Td (- Difficulty: Moderate) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 498.6 Td (- Best for: Those comfortable with 16:8 wanting more benefits) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 470.8 Td (20:4 \(Warrior Diet\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 454.8 Td (- Fast for 20 hours, eat within 4-hour window) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 440.8 Td (- Example: Eat 4pm-8pm \(one large meal + snack\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 426.8 Td (- Difficulty: Challenging) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 412.8 Td (- Best for: Experienced fasters, those who prefer one big meal) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 385.0 Td (5:2 \(Modified Fasting\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 369.0 Td (- Eat normally 5 days, restrict to 500-600 calories on 2 non-consecutive days) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 355.0 Td (- Example: Fast on Monday and Thursday) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 341.0 Td (- Difficulty: Moderate) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 327.0 Td (- Best for: Those who prefer not fasting daily) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 299.2 Td (Alternate Day Fasting \(ADF\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 283.2 Td (- Alternate between normal eating days and fasting/very low calorie days) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 269.2 Td (- Difficulty: Hard) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 255.2 Td (- Best for: Quick results, experienced fasters) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 227.4 Td (OMAD \(One Meal A Day\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 211.4 Td (- Fast for 23 hours, one large meal) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 197.4 Td (- Difficulty: Very challenging) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 183.4 Td (- Best for: Very experienced, those who thrive on simplicity) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 153.6 Td (My Chosen Method) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 135.6 Td (Method: _________________) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 121.6 Td (Eating window: ___:___ to ___:___) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 107.6 Td (Fasting hours: ___) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 93.6 Td (Start date: __/__/____) Tj ET
