BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Chapter 3: Getting Started Plan) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Gradual Adaptation Schedule) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 652.2 Td (Week 1: 12:12 \(ease in\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 636.2 Td (- Stop eating after dinner \(e.g., 8pm\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 622.2 Td (- Don't eat until 8am \(12-hour fast\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 608.2 Td (- This is natural for many people) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 590.2 Td (Week 2: 14:10) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 574.2 Td (- Push breakfast back 2 hours \(10am\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 560.2 Td (- Notice: You're probably not truly hungry at your old breakfast time) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 542.2 Td (Week 3: 16:8) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 526.2 Td (- Full 16:8 protocol) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 512.2 Td (- First meal at noon \(or your chosen time\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 498.2 Td (- Last meal by 8pm) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 480.2 Td (Week 4+: Maintain or extend) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 464.2 Td (- Stick with 16:8 or experiment with longer fasts) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 450.2 Td (- Listen to your body) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 420.4 Td (What Breaks a Fast?) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 398.4 Td (Won't Break Your Fast \(okay during fasting window\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 382.4 Td (- Water \(plain, sparkling, mineral\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 368.4 Td (- Black coffee \(no cream, sugar, or sweetener\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 354.4 Td (- Plain tea \(green, black, herbal\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 340.4 Td (- Salt/electrolytes) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 322.4 Td (WILL Break Your Fast) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 306.4 Td (- Any calories \(even small amounts\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 292.4 Td (- Cream or milk in coffee) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 278.4 Td (- Diet soda \(debated, but insulin response possible\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 264.4 Td (- Supplements with calories \(fish oil, gummies\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 250.4 Td (- Bone broth \(technically, though some allow it\)) Tj ET
endstream
