BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (What to Eat \(Quality Matters\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.2 Td (IF works best when combined with nutritious food. Don't use it as an excuse to eat poorly) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.2 Td (during your eating window.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 614.4 Td (Breaking Your Fast \(First Meal\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 598.4 Td (- Start with something gentle \(not a huge heavy meal\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 584.4 Td (- Protein first \(stabilizes blood sugar\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 570.4 Td (- Include healthy fat \(satiety\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 556.4 Td (- Add vegetables \(fiber and nutrients\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 542.4 Td (- Avoid pure sugar/carbs as first food \(causes crash\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 514.6 Td (Ideal Break-Fast Meals) Tj ET
