82 0 obj
<< /Length 3102 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Frequently Asked Questions) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Q: Won't I lose muscle while fasting?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 660.2 Td (No, if you eat adequate protein during your eating window and do resistance training. IF) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.2 Td (actually increases growth hormone, which helps preserve muscle. Muscle loss happens with) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.2 Td (chronic undereating, not time-restricted eating.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 604.4 Td (Q: Can I fast every day?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (Yes, methods like 16:8 are designed for daily use and are safe long-term for most healthy) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 574.4 Td (adults. Listen to your body - some people benefit from 1-2 non-fasting days per week.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 546.6 Td (Q: Why am I not losing weight with IF?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.6 Td (Common reasons: Overeating during eating window, not in a calorie deficit overall, too) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 516.6 Td (many processed foods, not enough sleep, high stress, or medical factors. IF is a tool, not) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 502.6 Td (magic.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 474.8 Td (Q: Is fasting safe for women?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 458.8 Td (Yes, but some women are more sensitive to fasting. Start conservatively \(12-14 hours\),) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 444.8 Td (avoid fasting around your period, and stop if menstrual irregularities occur.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 430.8 Td (Pregnant/nursing women should not fast.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 403.0 Td (Q: Does coffee break a fast?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 387.0 Td (Black coffee \(no cream, sugar, or sweetener\) does not break a fast. It actually enhances) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 373.0 Td (fat burning and suppresses appetite. Keep it to 1-2 cups to avoid cortisol spikes.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 345.2 Td (Q: Can I drink water during fasting?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 329.2 Td (Yes! Drink plenty of water during fasting. Add a pinch of salt for electrolytes. Sparkling) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 315.2 Td (water, black coffee, and plain tea are all fine.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 287.4 Td (Q: How long until I see results?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 271.4 Td (Many people notice improved energy and mental clarity within the first week. Weight loss) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 257.4 Td (typically becomes visible at 2-4 weeks. Body composition changes take 4-8 weeks.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 229.6 Td (Q: Is IF better than calorie counting?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 213.6 Td (Both can work. Many people find IF easier because it simplifies decision-making \(you just) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 199.6 Td (watch the clock\). Some people do best combining both. Choose what's sustainable for you.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 171.8 Td (Q: What if I feel dizzy or weak?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 155.8 Td (Initial adjustment is normal. Ensure adequate electrolytes \(sodium, potassium, magnesium\),) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 141.8 Td (stay hydrated, and ease into longer fasts. If severe, shorten your fasting window or break) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 127.8 Td (your fast.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 100.0 Td (Q: Can I fast with diabetes?) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
