stream
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 720.0 Td (Type 2 diabetes patients may benefit from IF, but MUST work with their doctor, especially) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 706.0 Td (if on insulin or sulfonylureas \(hypoglycemia risk\). Never fast without medical guidance if) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 692.0 Td (diabetic.) Tj ET
endstream
